Simple and pedantic backup Git repositories


Easy config. Detailed log.
Auto Clone/Update repository (full and incremental backup).
Auto backup and prune all branches. Auto and manual choise compressor for archives.
Circular buffer for archives (default disabled).


1) Get this: git clone git://github.com/progman/git_backup.git
2) Just run git_backup.example.sh for simple start
3) Use it!
